</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top">
<p>Ethics and privacy:</p>
</td>
<td valign="top">
<p>Feedback is given direct to the individual learner, not shared or distributed to others.</p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top">
